data.description: Nothing to do here, just move in and enjoy. Meticulously maintained. Overlook the huge totally fenced backyard from the 27x15 deck. Large oversized and insulated garage with enough room for a truck. Many updates including garage doors, front steps, sidewalk, concrete driveway, central air, siding, facia. Convenient to shopping, transportation, and Aurelia Park.
